3. cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) - The paper discusses the appearance of visemes on the lips, which is a visual feature. 
4. cs.LG (Machine Learning) - The paper proposes a new algorithm for constructing phoneme-to-viseme mappings, which is a machine learning task.
